=== reference management software
fileformat supports (export/ import): bibtex, endnote, medline, mods xml, RIS, docbook, COins, rdf, TEI, rtf, pdf, copac, csa, ISI, SciFinder, Ovid
Citation styles: APA, Chicago/Turabian, Harvard, MLA, IEEE, BMJ,
feeds: RSS, Atom
database connectivty: Arxiv, Citeseer, IEEE xplore, PubMed, ACM, GoogleScholar
user-specific-permissions, password protection

